Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.94,0:00:04.20,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等 等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.82,0:00:06.83,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,要带我去哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.83,0:00:07.95,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,那里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.83,0:00:13.40,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这些僵尸有多少具…个…人啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.40,0:00:14.40,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.40,0:00:15.83,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我没数过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.83,0:00:17.43,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他们以前是人吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.43,0:00:20.20,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,因为7G事件才变成了僵尸？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:21.18,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.66,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,「谁知道」是什么啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:23.95,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你要拿我怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.95,0:00:25.01,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吃掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.01,0:00:25.75,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.78,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吃吗？毕竟是僵尸嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.78,0:00:28.90,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:30.55,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,明明你吃的是罐头！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:31.75,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这不对吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:34.60,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我没法照顾到每个僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:36.31,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你不是女王吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:38.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,至少管好跟班吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:40.54,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,还有我的内裤要露出来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:41.14,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,{\an8}内裤…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:46.56,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你不逃的话 我就给你解开绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:47.84,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不会逃的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.84,0:00:48.99,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,绝对不会吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.99,0:00:50.05,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,绝对不会！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:52.21,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,解开绳子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:53.69,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,让她下来走
