Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:28.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:30.92,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,这样从远处也能看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:33.57,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,绝对不能走散！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.93,0:02:35.41,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,走散就死定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:36.60,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,说得对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:38.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,尤其是晶你很容易会分散注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.35,0:02:39.54,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我说的是你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:41.06,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}好啦好啦 该走了
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.84,0:02:44.30,Signs_WText,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\bord0.267\fs84\pos(1127.697,825.779)}第7话  会笑的僵尸可不是僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:42.44,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}要出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.41,0:02:47.77,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是要怎么找到静留呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.77,0:02:50.07,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,如果僵尸已经抓到她了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:51.75,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,僵尸昼伏夜出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.80,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.44,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,僵尸视力不好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:56.04,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:57.96,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,僵尸喜欢脑髓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.96,0:02:58.56,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:02:59.70,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:00.11,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\bord1.111\c&H8A302D&\3c&HB2B4AF&\an7}铝箔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:02.48,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,先这样 然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.20,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,看上去就像大脑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:05.61,Default,Group,0,0,0,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.48,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,僵尸抵抗不了脑髓的诱惑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.90,0:03:09.51,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,只要看到脑髓 就会向其靠拢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.51,0:03:10.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,所以 万一遇到紧急状况
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.90,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,就扔出脑髓争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:24.45,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,根本没争取到时间啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:25.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,反而还吸引他们了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.39,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不要快速运动！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:27.96,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:30.65,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,装成僵尸就好 他们是认不出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:31.97,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,僵尸动作很慢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.93,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,僵尸…不会尖叫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:48.88,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,被怀疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.38,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,完全在怀疑我们啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:52.13,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我现在就引开他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:55.68,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,太近了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:56.95,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,闭嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.27,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶 玲实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.27,0:04:02.54,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,趁现在！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:14.65,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,忍耐住啊 忍耐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:17.26,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我知道 但是这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.82,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,僵尸不会攻击同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.82,0:04:21.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就算这样 画花脸真能让他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.11,0:04:25.96,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,起效了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.71,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,慢慢远离吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:30.70,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.13,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那是静留的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.59,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,果然静留也变成了僵尸…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.97,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,还不能确定事实如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:52.27,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是静留变得只想着脑髓 那该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.27,0:04:53.95,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,忘记叶香的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.95,0:04:55.73,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不会的 这不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:56.80,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:08.49,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,神舆？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:09.60,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:10.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,静留在这
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:11.37,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,波奇也在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.54,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,变蓝了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:13.80,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,茶色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:14.63,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,茶色？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:16.07,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,已经腐烂了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.07,0:05:17.44,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,没啊 毛还很浓密
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.44,0:05:17.96,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.34,0:05:19.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,说的是波奇吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:21.61,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,才不是！问的是人啦！静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.61,0:05:24.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,哇 脸看上去挺正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:25.29,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,确实是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.69,0:05:27.93,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,还没变成僵尸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:30.67,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那她为什么还老实地待在那？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.67,0:05:32.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,以静留的性格 她应该大闹一通才对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:34.28,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说得对呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.69,0:05:36.67,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 她吓了一跳 大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:38.34,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,摔倒了屁股着地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.34,0:05:39.95,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,这么大的动作看得到的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:41.12,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,她想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:41.97,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,喂 静——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.21,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,僵尸模式啦！僵尸模式！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:47.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？很痒？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:48.58,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,开始变僵尸了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:49.36,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:52.12,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,她大概在问我们变成僵尸了 还是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.95,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 因为我们涂脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:56.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,抚子你最不妙吧？群青色的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.84,0:05:57.89,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,群青色…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:05:59.88,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,声音听上去也像僵尸一样浑浊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.12,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,是不是水蓝色好点？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:01.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.16,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,没法动眼球？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.16,0:06:04.30,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,胳膊要掉了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.65,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,脑子不够了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.65,0:06:07.52,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,完蛋了完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:08.19,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.56,0:06:12.46,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,那三个人怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:15.80,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:19.58,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,这样啊…原人类的原朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:20.34,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,「原」是什么意思啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.32,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an3}「朋友」是什么啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.32,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an1}「人类」是什么啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.32,0:06:23.47,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,还是说原朋友的人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:27.44,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,都不是的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:29.42,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,原人类的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:31.18,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,人类朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.18,0:06:33.07,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别在意这些细节嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不管原不原啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:36.06,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:37.90,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我绝不容忍忤逆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.12,0:06:41.65,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,还能说话就意味着 没完全变成僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.10,0:06:43.90,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,还是说伪装成僵尸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.12,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不回答？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:48.17,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:51.30,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,是不是僵尸 只要问问你们的身体就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:52.57,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,身体？！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:53.02,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.73,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,把那个准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.12,0:06:56.30,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,铁处女？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:57.54,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,法拉里斯的铜牛？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.30,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,犹大的摇篮？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:03.30,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,乌冬？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.30,0:07:04.81,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,这可不是普通的乌冬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.50,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,这是武藏名产
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:08.55,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,加入时令蔬菜的粗面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:10.63,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,把猪肉和味噌一起煮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.68,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,口感劲道的乡村乌冬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:15.32,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,再加一点七味粉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:24.59,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,吃一口筋道的面条 喝一口汤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:26.84,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,再吃一口猪肉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.50,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,又在吃独食哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:31.37,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我是女王 所以是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:34.24,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,僵尸一般是没食欲的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:38.50,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,既然对煮乌冬面没反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.38,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,看来你们似乎确实是僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:42.28,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,对对 是僵尸啦僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.28,0:07:44.39,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们是僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:46.85,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,但我还不能确信！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.53,0:08:05.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,啊 又死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.83,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,菜鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.34,0:08:12.76,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,因为我是女王 所以不用和人换着玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.71,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:15.49,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要更依靠手腕发力来装填…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.49,0:08:16.44,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.47,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 好气…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:19.65,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,好气？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.65,0:08:21.41,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,僵尸可不会烦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:23.01,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,更不用说生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:24.43,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.43,0:08:25.55,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.55,0:08:26.78,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,要玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.81,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我…不玩！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:30.34,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,僵尸不会玩游戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.60,0:08:32.85,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,但如果是女王的命令的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.72,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,可恶！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:36.32,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,混账！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.33,0:08:37.92,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,吃我这招！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:39.09,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,爆头啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.09,0:08:42.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,抚子一玩游戏就会切换人格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:44.27,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,还有握弓的时候也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:46.47,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,要是能在游戏里配上一把弓就无敌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:49.09,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,死吧你！真难缠！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:50.01,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:51.29,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,区区僵尸！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:53.13,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你玩得还真不错呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.75,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,托您的福…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.55,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,作为僵尸 你的反应速度够快的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.02,0:09:03.42,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那是因为 你看…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.42,0:09:06.91,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她刚变僵尸 反射神经还没失灵！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:07.43,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:08.40,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.31,0:09:13.65,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,僵尸可不会笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:18.00,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,会笑的僵尸可不是僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.50,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.50,0:09:20.59,Default,Group,0,0,0,,是说？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:22.58,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,人类
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:25.51,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,绑起来！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.05,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.17,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,和她们一起的话 那你也是敌人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.90,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我要吃光你们的脑子！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.90,0:09:32.76,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吃得到就来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:42.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,欧——拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:47.26,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:48.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:50.77,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 掉下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.25,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,难道说他们超弱的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.25,0:09:53.35,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,感觉我们也能上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:57.16,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,真厉害啊 晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.97,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,明明害怕妖怪 面对僵尸却没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:02.19,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嘿——！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:09.86,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,能赢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.17,0:10:18.64,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶为啥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:22.67,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,粘回去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.34,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.81,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,无限僵尸！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:27.03,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,僵尸是死不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:27.83,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,卑劣！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:29.52,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,这就是僵尸的生态
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.52,0:10:30.98,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,有什么卑劣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.98,0:10:33.68,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,生态？性…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:37.28,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,{\an8}我们正好收到了迁徙僵尸的目击情报
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.28,0:10:39.09,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,迁徙僵尸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.31,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,他们很难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.31,0:10:43.25,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,无论被打倒多少次都会重新站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:44.72,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,虽然弱小但是不灭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:46.76,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,那要怎么对付他们？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:51.83,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,这是没有被确证过的情报 僵尸对「性」很弱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:52.66,Default,Group,0,0,0,,「生」？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:55.24,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,啊 是说活着的东西吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:56.78,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但他们会袭击人类吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.78,0:10:59.57,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,不是 这个 你们别当真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:00.12,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:03.33,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「性」是说性爱或者厄洛斯之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:04.37,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:06.55,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,别啊 是说僵尸都喜欢色色吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:09.84,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,不是 是说他们不擅长对付这个 弱点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.84,0:11:12.75,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,僵尸的存在即是死本身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:14.02,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,就是塔那托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.02,0:11:15.90,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,阴 破坏 灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.42,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,相对应的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:18.01,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,厄洛斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.83,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}重视性爱的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:21.74,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,晶又在说怪话了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:25.95,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}就是对善与美以及活物的重视
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:22.94,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,嘘！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.47,0:11:27.08,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我也不知道她在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:28.64,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,现在是在说僵尸的话题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.93,0:11:29.85,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.92,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,不对上僵尸是最好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:34.67,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,但近距离接触的话 静止不动是铁则
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.18,0:11:36.30,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,刚刚说的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:39.13,Default,Neko,0,0,0,,归根结底也只是僵尸的原理原则之一
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:44.17,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,色——情——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:43.63,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\an8}抚—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.64,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不对 不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:47.63,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,是那个啦 是厄洛斯的话题呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:48.77,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,色、色情？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.39,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:51.51,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那个 你别误会啊 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.51,0:11:53.19,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,猫哥提到的那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.19,0:11:54.40,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,对 就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:55.57,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,晶 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.57,0:11:57.06,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,说点厄洛斯的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:57.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,{\pos(1237.333,1050)}啥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:57.99,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\pos(368,1050)}啥？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:12:00.08,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,什么都行！快说！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:02.34,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,厄洛斯的事情 厄洛斯的事情……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.34,0:12:04.57,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,对了 英国文学里的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:14.15,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「梅勒斯执拗地以淫靡的手法\N沿着她腰部优美的曲线往下爱抚」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:20.29,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「然后他的手指越发地深入\N近乎要触碰到那敏感的花蕊」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.29,0:12:24.47,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「康妮现在无法反抗 甚至无暇感到羞涩」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:29.27,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「只能张开那雅致的两腿 将她的一切袒露于他」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:35.22,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,「她感受到了 这个男人正在彰显着自己身为雄性的力量」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.40,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}「在身体中 一个巨物在粗暴地进入」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.51,0:12:36.46,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,好色哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:37.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,晶 你居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:41.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,等等 抚子 你笑得好下流！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:44.98,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}「她全身都感受到了这份快乐」……
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:48.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,它在笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:50.37,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是说僵尸不会笑吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:52.54,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,爆炸了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.01,0:12:57.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,晶 你太厉害了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:13:00.58,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,为什么她们会知道僵尸的弱点？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.98,0:13:02.62,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\bord1.111\c&H729544&\3c&HB2B4AF&\an7}遮瑕棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.21,0:13:12.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,再来点色色的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.84,0:13:14.04,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,猎奇的不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:14.73,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.73,0:13:15.85,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我已经没有点子了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你再想想 编点出来！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:17.89,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.89,0:13:19.28,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,你才该想一想！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:21.30,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,色色的事情 色色的事情……
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:24.15,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,花…花…花…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:25.93,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,花枝乱颤！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.68,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,呜哇 感觉有点色诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.80,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,桑…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.73,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,桑间濮上！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:33.03,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,什么濮上？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:34.91,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,扭…扭…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:35.59,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,扭来扭去!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.99,0:13:40.89,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,抚子 扭来扭去才不色啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:54.82,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,唉 浑身都黏糊糊的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:57.00,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果说「泥泞不堪」会不会很色？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.00,0:13:59.22,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,确实可能这样会更色一点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.22,0:14:00.80,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,扭…扭…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.80,0:14:02.51,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,扭扭捏捏 会觉得色吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.51,0:14:03.88,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不好说呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.50,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,视情况而定？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:06.18,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.02,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,吵吵闹闹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:10.23,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:12.49,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,郁郁寡欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:13.62,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,磨磨蹭蹭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.88,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,碌碌无为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.88,0:14:16.01,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,忧心忡忡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:19.74,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,低头认错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.91,0:14:25.48,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留 这个就留到跟叶香再会时说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:37.68,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我们的列车在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:38.93,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,吾野在这个方向
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur0.267\fnComic Sans MS\c&H323232&\frz29.05\fax0.49\pos(417.362,530.667)}我们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.44,0:14:41.90,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur0.267\fnComic Sans MS\c&H323232&\frz29.05\fax0.49\pos(1114.387,204)}神树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:40.17,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那边是去池袋的路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.90,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,然后僵尸在这一带
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:42.85,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.85,0:14:44.52,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我们要一头扎进尸群里？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.52,0:14:45.54,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,就凭着我们的列车？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.54,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,嘎吱嘎吱地冲上去？再撞个粉身碎骨？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.43,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我有点…绝对不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:51.04,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对了 快到五点了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:52.49,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,得跟善治郎先生定期联络
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:55.19,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生说不定知道很多色色的事情！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.19,0:14:57.04,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,什么？知道一首歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.05,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:14:58.83,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,抚子！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.83,0:15:00.21,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,我把这首歌复述一遍 你记下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:00.99,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:03.97,Default,Zenjiro,0,0,0,,那么便由我献上一曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.30,0:15:20.73,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我可不会放走你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.25,0:15:22.87,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,僵尸们 上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:24.10,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,抓住那些人类！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:30.83,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,诶 那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.49,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果不起作用怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:34.12,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,也只能试试了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.49,0:15:43.51,Default,Group,0,0,0,,今晚是黏黏糊糊的交合之节
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.51,0:15:48.50,Default,Group,0,0,0,,迎面而来的内人楚楚动人\N剥落衣服 敞开身体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.50,0:15:51.08,Default,Group,0,0,0,,嘿！一个在吸 一个在推 啪啪作响！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:53.62,Default,Group,0,0,0,,啪啪 啪啪啪 啪啪作响！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:54.09,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,再来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.09,0:15:56.47,Default,Group,0,0,0,,啪啪 啪啪啪 啪啪作响！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.79,0:16:04.73,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:06.48,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,起效了起效了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:08.10,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,善治郎先生太厉害了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.10,0:16:10.60,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这是不是善治郎先生第一次帮上我们的忙？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:16.21,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,他们不肯靠近过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.84,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,那到底是个啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.84,0:16:21.86,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,说到底结成种群迁徙根本不像是僵尸会有的习性
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.86,0:16:23.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,诶？是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.12,0:16:27.85,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,毕竟 这不就意味着\N他们存在着支配与隶属的命令系统嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:30.77,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,僵尸原来也有阶级的概念吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:31.97,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.97,0:16:34.17,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,他们还服从于僵尸的女王诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.94,0:16:36.23,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,等等 静留
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:37.15,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:38.54,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我去跟女王谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:39.28,Default,Group,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.88,0:16:41.91,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,谈谈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.30,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不行不行不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:46.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,你真觉得能和僵尸沟通吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.00,0:16:48.98,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你们先听我说 那女王应该不是僵尸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:49.60,Default,Group,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:52.43,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,只有她一个人在吃正常的食物 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.43,0:16:53.46,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,比如说乌冬面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.46,0:16:55.12,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,虽然没给我们吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.90,0:16:58.24,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那不是因为她是女王吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:00.25,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,这个多半只是她的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.83,0:17:03.78,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,她肯定也不想暴露自己是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:05.13,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,这个确实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.13,0:17:07.24,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,她一直在扮演女王吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:09.00,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,也就是说 可以用这个来威胁她？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:11.74,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,但是 如果她真的就是僵尸呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.42,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,真的就是僵尸的话 就和她战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:18.31,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,就算是女王 粉身碎骨后也不可能复活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:19.42,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,粉身碎骨？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.42,0:17:21.44,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,别小看吾野柔术！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:22.64,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,我和你一起去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:24.92,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,如果说静留有吾野柔术
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:28.60,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,那我也有吾野弓术和死亡之屋的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.99,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,等等！我们有话要讲！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:36.66,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.41,0:17:41.32,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,停下！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.65,0:17:48.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.43,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,什么为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:52.55,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,是因为暴露了就会被吃掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.09,0:17:59.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.111\c&H729544&\3c&HB2B4AF&\an7}遮瑕棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:17:59.98,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:01.14,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.67,0:18:03.58,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,大家都怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.02,0:18:17.98,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,什 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.98,0:18:19.15,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.73,0:18:23.08,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不要 内裤全露出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.79,0:18:27.54,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,难道是因为内裤？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.54,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你从那时开始就一直在当女王？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.76,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,欺骗那些僵尸?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.76,0:18:35.25,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,玲实！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.35,0:18:38.01,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,与其说是欺骗 不如说不得不那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:40.35,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,黑木家最近的车站是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:41.40,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,保谷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:43.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你没想过回去吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:45.77,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我是有想过 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:48.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,因为不能被僵尸察觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:51.35,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,也有这个原因 不过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:18:57.24,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不许动！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.02,0:19:05.29,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我得回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.10,0:19:40.81,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你们在等我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.78,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,就算发霉了也不认输 你们很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.78,0:19:54.00,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不愧是女王的部下！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.71,0:20:02.20,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:04.12,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,真好啊 主从关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:07.35,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,然后你就带着僵尸们四处迁徙到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:11.49,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,不这样做的话他们就会发霉然后粉碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:12.39,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:14.52,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你原来还是个不错的女王啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:16.18,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我只是不得已而为之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.41,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.69,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,你就是个好女王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.91,0:20:21.03,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:23.31,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,我们要去池袋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.71,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,黑木木你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.71,0:20:26.26,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,不要太自来熟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.26,0:20:28.00,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,没事的 因为我们是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:29.29,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:32.22,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,要一起走吗 黑木木？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:35.67,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,和朋友…去池袋…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.52,0:20:38.76,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:44.62,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,那可不行 因为我是女王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:45.66,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.66,0:20:47.25,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,之前扣留你们是我错了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.37,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,因为难得见到一次人类
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:52.48,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,就忍不住多说了几句话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:57.26,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,但既然你们有目的地 那我就不应该妨碍你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.24,0:21:01.28,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我会好好告诫僵尸不要袭击人类的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.75,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,即使如此 你们还是会被畏惧被讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:06.04,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,甚至可能会被攻击的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.25,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,已经习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:07.98,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:11.49,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,但是现在的我已经不是以前的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:13.37,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,而且我还有这些僵尸同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:15.69,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,你们不需要太过担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:16.84,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:21.33,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,路上多加小心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:24.33,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,我听说池袋也有其它的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.33,0:21:25.25,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,再见！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.65,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,回来的时候再来找你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:27.91,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,注意你的内裤！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.91,0:21:31.14,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,只需手腕的一点小动作就能完成换弹！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:33.25,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,{\an8}第一章通关加油啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:34.27,Default,Kuroki,0,0,0,,要对女王多加警惕！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:41.23,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,黑木木以前被霸凌过吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:42.94,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,哈？完全没关系吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:44.14,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,有关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.14,0:21:44.83,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:47.45,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,过去的事情连接着当下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:49.24,Shizuru,Shizuru,0,0,0,,然后成为未来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.29,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,不管是好事还是坏事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.58,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,无论贫穷还是富有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:54.20,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,那个不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:55.61,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}为啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:56.93,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}那 阿猫阿狗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.10,0:21:57.48,Nadeshiko,Nadeshiko,0,0,0,,静留
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:21:57.60,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}更不对了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.60,0:21:58.16,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}诶？！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:21:59.84,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}那就 对牛弹琴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:00.97,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}完全不对！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:02.23,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}性欲不如食欲？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.23,0:22:03.47,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}根本不沾边！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.34,0:22:09.97,Signs_WText,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(1025,1)\bord0.2\pos(1000,811)}{\fs98}距离池袋还有14站
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:05.83,Reimi,Reimi,0,0,0,,{\an8}偷鸡不成蚀把米？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.83,0:22:06.38,Akira,Akira,0,0,0,,{\an8}不对！
